      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "韦陀",
        "杨任",
        "龙须虎",
        "金吒",
        "木吒",
        "哪吒",
        "雷震子"
      ],
      "text": "请了！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00013",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨戬"
      ],
      "text": "今日师叔发兵，命你我两厢伺候。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00014",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "韦陀",
        "杨任",
        "龙须虎",
        "金吒",
        "木吒",
        "哪吒",
        "雷震子"
      ],
      "text": "请。（杨戬、韦陀、杨任、龙须虎、金吒、木吒、哪吒、雷震子分归两边站。四文堂、四大铠、四上手、姜子牙同上。）",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00015",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "昆仑嫡派，顺天命宇宙重开。甲子年，成汤衰败。戊午期周室运来。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00016",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨戬",
        "韦陀",
        "杨任",
        "龙须虎",
        "金吒",
        "木吒",
        "哪吒",
        "雷震子"
      ],
      "text": "参见师叔。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00017",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "站立两厢。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00018",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨戬",
        "韦陀",
        "杨任",
        "龙须虎",
        "金吒",
        "木吒",
        "哪吒",
        "雷震子"
      ],
      "text": "啊。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00019",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "两仪四象分阴阳，女娲炼石补上苍。三教共议封神榜，吾奉法旨灭成汤。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00020",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "老夫姜子牙，前奉王命攻打潼关，不料被余化龙暗用瘟药将我军迷倒，多亏慈航道人相救，方得无事。今日整齐兵将与他见个胜负。众弟子听吾一令！",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00021",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨戬",
        "韦陀",
        "杨任",
        "龙须虎",
        "金吒",
        "木吒",
        "哪吒",
        "雷震子"
      ],
      "text": "啊。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00022",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄正板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "自三皇开关后乾坤荡荡，尧传舜舜传禹降至商汤。殷纣王宠妲己酒色淫荡，诛发妻杀亲子令人惨伤。女娲庙去拈香欺灭神像，粉壁墙题诗句触怒上苍。女娲氏聚齐了妖群一党，灭成汤兴周室国运永昌。有老夫奉法旨肩背神榜，保武王开山河一统无疆。临潼关余化龙兵多将广，用瘟药迷将士险把命亡。感天恩不绝我周营兵将，解三灾救八难多亏慈航。吾今日整雄威重发兵将，托上苍保佑着得胜疆场。",
      "text_length": 176
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00023",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "杨戬。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00024",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨戬"
      ],
      "text": "在。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00025",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄正板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "仗玄功多变化奇才无两，移深山倒大海妙术高强。此一番去出兵谁人敢挡，三尖刀嚎天犬带在身边。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00026",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨戬"
      ],
      "text": "领法旨。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00027",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "韦陀。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00028",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韦陀"
      ],
      "text": "在。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00029",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "你七世神通体天地恩养，自幼儿修道法显应无疆。降魔杵打神将天仙难挡，建奇功吾将你威名表扬。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00030",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韦陀"
      ],
      "text": "领法旨。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00031",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "杨任。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
