      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨任"
      ],
      "text": "在。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00033",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "你在那紫阳洞修成法像，蒙师恩赐与你宝扇神枪。到阵前必须要神眼观望，管教那余化龙无处躲藏。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00034",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨任"
      ],
      "text": "领法旨。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00035",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "金吒。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00036",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "你本是将门子英雄上将，一朝君一朝臣子胜父强。今日里逢劫运乾坤改样，必须要秉忠心扶保武王。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00037",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
