      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "哪吒"
      ],
      "text": "在。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00044",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜子牙"
      ],
      "text": "你本是莲花体变化多广，乾坤圈火尖枪盖世无双。风炎轮如闪电霞光万丈，生三头并六臂无人能当。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001019_e00045",
      "play_id": "02001019",
      "scene_id": "02001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
